<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Html To Node</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 42px;
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 18px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      p:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02);
      }

      h4 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #007bff;
        margin: 15px 0;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #e9f1ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      /* Add some padding to the main content */
      main {
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      /* Footer styling */
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }

      /* Responsive adjustments */
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 32px;
        }

        h4 {
          font-size: 18px;
        }

        p {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Welcome to [Your Website Name], where we are committed to delivering a seamless user experience through dynamic content and personalized services. Our platform offers a variety of features, including a detailed Product Catalog linked directly to our database, allowing you to explore our diverse range of products effortlessly.</p>
      
      <h4>1. Company/Project Background</h4>
      <p>Details about the company or the purpose of the project. Here, you can share the vision and mission that drives your organization.</p>

      <h4>2. Product or Service Descriptions</h4>
      <p>Information on the products or services offered. Highlight key offerings that set you apart from the competition.</p>

      <h4>3. Team Members</h4>
      <p>Introduce the team behind the website. Share a bit about the members, their roles, and contributions.</p>

      <h4>4. Technology Stack</h4>
      <p>Technical details about the tools and frameworks used in development. Mention the technologies that power your platform.</p>

      <h4>5. User Guidance</h4>
      <p>Instructions on how to navigate or use the website's features. Provide tips for users to get the most out of your site.</p>
    </main>

    <footer>
      &copy; 2024 [Your Website Name]. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
